    "name": "SecureTask",
    "description": "StartFragment\n\nSecureTask API\n\nA full-stack task management system with JWT Authentication and Role-Based Access Control.\n\nFeatures:\n\n- User Authentication\n    \n- Protected Routes\n    \n- Role-Based Access (User/Admin)\n    \n- Task CRUD Operations\n    \n- Admin Task Management\n    \n\nAuthentication:  \nJWT tokens are stored in HTTP-only cookies.\n\nRoles:  \nUser:\n\n- Manage own tasks\n    \n\nAdmin:\n\n- Manage all tasks\n    \n- View all users\n    \n- Delete users\n    \n\nEndFragment",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "49724668",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/49724668-916d5506-f9fb-4842-998f-3136c09de168?source=collection_link"
